                        <li>I've had internship as a baker at <a title="Bakery that no longer exist sadly" class="text-decoration-none link-info">Sockerbagarnas</a>.</li>
                        <li>I've had internship as a chef at <a title="A school in a suburb called Åby north fom Norrköping" class="text-decoration-none link-info">Åbymo Skolan</a>.</li>
                        <li>I've had internship as a chef at <a title="A pre-school in Norrköping" class="text-decoration-none link-info">Förskola Berlocken</a>.</li>
