            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row m-2"></div>
        <div class="card-text col">

            @* Interests *@
            <div class="list-group">
                <div class="list-group-item">
                    Interests
                </div>
                <div class="list-group-item">
                    I've always had a strong interest in gaming and remember when I was a child plaing Super Mario Bros. 
                    for the <a title="Nintendo Entertainment System" class="text-decoration-none link-info">NES</a> for the first time in the early to mid 90s.<br />
                    Now however I am mostly playing PC Games like <a title="An online role playing game" class="text-decoration-none link-info">World of Warcraft</a>,
                    <a title="Extremely laidback and fun farming RPG" class="text-decoration-none link-info">Stardew Valley</a> 
