                    Other hobbies I enjoy consist of Cooking. Despite having worked with food most of my worklike, 
                    I still do enjoy cooking for and entertaining guests.<br />
                    I also enjoy Reading <a title="Japanese Comics" class="text-decoration-none link-info">Manga</a>, especially when commuting, great way to make the commute go a little faster.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text col">

            @* Finishing Words *@
            <div class="list-group">
                <div class="list-group-item">
                    Finishing Words
                </div>
                <div class="list-group-item">
                    Thank you for taking an interest and reading about myself!<br />
                    See you on the flip side!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
